Anson B SAMS Dr

Mrs Lancaster
--------
Sarah was post master at Marshall NC at one time. She was 16 years. old when
she married Dr Anson B Sams and they had 8 children. She was also his nurse in
the Civil War where and when he was a surgeon. She lived in VA during the War
and on Patton Ave in Asheville NC weith her family after war. D and is bur at
Eatenton, GA.
